des:
Are you a huge The Walking Dead fan? Then you need the Undead Walking Flash Briefing Skill by FanSided to get the latest news, opinions and rumors on The Walking Dead. 

Undead Walking is a Walking Dead news site brought to you by the FanSided Network dedicated to providing top-notch news, views and original content. This site also serves as a community for like-minded fans to come together to catch up on the latest news and to discuss their passion.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
